                            <h3>Meet the Author</h3>
                        <p>Hi! I'm Marina and I like to call myself a Lifelong Learner. 
                            My story could have started with "once upon a time" because I have lived my first years of life in an era before internet, computers and mobile phones. 
                            Can you imagine that? Even for me now, looking back, it seems like an old movie watched somewhere and not my reality.</p>
                        <p>Two years ago I have received this message: <em><q>Dream your own dreams, my darling!</q></em>. 
                            I realised that my dreams are not the same anymore and I had no clue which are the new ones.
                            It was clear to me that I have to take some time off, get in touch with myself and learn how to dream again. 
                            And this is what I am continuously doing since that moment.</p>
